
"We can take a nap if you want?" She looks up and nods slightly, then yawns.
I re-adjust by sliding down more into the couch and laying Alex directly on top of my chest and between my legs. She wraps her arms around my chest and I pull the blanket up to cover her shoulders and kiss her hair.
"I won't let anything happen to you Alex, I promise." I say right when she closes her eyes.
She smiles and nuzzles into my chest and I close my eyes and fall into a deep sleep with my Mrs All American.

